//========================================================================
// HUMANS - List of NAMES, MODELS and SOUNDS
//========================================================================
// Description:
//
// names <lang-id> {}
//	A list of actor-names for the given language.
//	Uses sub-lists as follows:
//		neutral {}
//		female {}
//		male {}
//		lastname {}
//		female_lastname {}
//		male_lastname {}
// actors <actor-id> {}
//	A List of model-paths with the following syntax:
//		<path/to/model> <model_file_name> <model_head_filename> <skinnumber>
//	Uses sub-lists as follows:
//		neutral {}
//		female {}
//		male {}
// teamdesc <actor-id> {}
//	Defines the values of such actor
// team <team-id> {{ }}
//	Defines which actors are in given team.
//	The list of actors in inside a second pair of {} (with no name)
// actorsounds <lang-id> {}
//	A list of soundfiles for the various sound-events. Syntax
//		<sound-event> <path/to/soundfile/soundfile>
//	Uses sub-lists as follows:
//		neutral {}
//		female {}
//		male {}
//	Possible sound-events are:
//		hurtsound
//		deathsound
//========================================================================

